SearchScreen.name: SearchScreen
SearchScreen.description: Search Screen contains both search and filter functions

HomeScreen.name: HomeScreen
HomeScreen.description: Home Screen contains top lists and search history

CarparkInfoScreen.name: CarparkInfoScreen
CarparkInfoScreen.description: Carpark Information Screen contains lots available, free parking timings etc. for a specific carpark

CarparkMapsScreen.name: CarparkMapsScreen
CarparkMapsScreen.description:
Carpark Maps screen contains map with markers of all carparks and list of all available carparks and free parking timings
On click of list element, it routes to carpark information screen.

HawkerMapsScreen.name: HawkerMapsScreen
HawkerMapsScreen.description: Hawker Maps contains all hawker centres in Singapore marked on map and list of all hawker centres and their respective closure dates.

OverallCarparkInfoScreen.name: OverallCarparkInfoScreen
OverallCarparkInfoScreen.description: Carpark Information Screen contains lots available, free parking timings etc. for a specific carpark

ResultsScreen.name: ResultsScreen
ResultsScreen.description: Results screen of hawker stalls upon search

InfoScreen.name: InfoScreen
InfoScreen.description: Hawker information Screen containing food categories, image of stall front, opening hours and how to get there.
